### Create product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: local-create-product

{
  "name": "Frozen Dumplings",
  "category": "Frozen Meals",
  "description": "Frozen prepared meal item",
  "metadata": {
    "coldChain": true,
    "packFormat": "bag"
  }
}

### List products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
X-Correlation-Id: local-list-products

### Create SKU
POST http://localhost:8080/api/skus
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: local-create-sku

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "skuCode": "FD-500G",
  "name": "Frozen Dumplings 500g",
  "unitOfMeasure": "pack",
  "storageClass": "FROZEN",
  "shelfLifeDays": 180,
  "barcode": "9550000000010"
}

### List SKUs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/skus
X-Correlation-Id: local-list-skus

### Get SKU
GET http://localhost:8080/api/skus/{{skuId}}
X-Correlation-Id: local-get-sku

### Update SKU status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/skus/{{skuId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: local-update-sku-status

{
  "status": "DISCONTINUED"
}
